oracle.olapi.metadata.mdm

Interface Mdm11_2_ObjectVisitor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Mdm10_1_0_3_ObjectVisitor, Mdm11_ObjectVisitor, MdmObjectVisitor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MdmBaseObjectVisitor

    public interface Mdm11_2_ObjectVisitor
extends Mdm11_ObjectVisitor
    An extension of the MdmObject visitor interfaces that has methods for visiting classes that the Oracle OLAP Java API adds in Oracle 11g, Release 2 (11.2).
